{
  "description": "A large container ship, identified as 'YANG MING', dominates the right side of the frame, partially submerged in water. The ship is primarily dark grey with a vibrant red hull below the waterline. The water's surface is highly reflective, creating a distorted mirror image of the ship and a dazzling array of colors\u2014reds, oranges, yellows, and blues\u2014that ripple across the water. The reflection appears almost abstract, resembling a painterly mosaic. The ship's structure includes multiple layers of containers and visible deck components. The angle suggests the ship is docked or slowly moving through the water. There's a slight blurring of the reflection due to the water's movement, enhancing the dynamic feel of the image.",
